{"tid":548804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美智庫：2020中共攻台勝算增","createTime":"2018-02-03T03:37:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-03T08:38:27.000Z","uid":46356,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4b80b40b0bea3bc51a86efc213d9b144de142917","tid":548804,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T03:37:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180203/20293960\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180203%2F20293960&d=zRDvmxCS8mYNeMIDAQYKsV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=14ed200d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180203%2F20293960&h=0cee1e9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180203/20293960</a><br />\n<strong>美智庫：2020中共攻台勝算增</strong><br />\n<br />\n美國著名防務智庫蘭德公司（RAND）最新報告稱，如果中國大陸2020年前後攻打台灣，成功可能性大大提高，因兩年後解放軍（圖）訊息戰、導彈火力、制空和登陸戰等方面，已有足夠實力與美軍抗衡，並可重創台軍。報告建議美國和盟友必須加大對台軍事投入。<br />\n<br />\n訊息戰有力與美抗衡<br />\n<br />\n報告認為，中國持續的軍事投入，在訓練和準備方面取得進步，台海兩岸雙方的勝算平衡正在向中國大陸一方傾斜。解放軍攻台有兩個的策略關鍵：在衝突發生時快速搶佔先機，以及在訊息戰方面搶先於美軍。解放軍有能力對美國海外軍事設施和航母進行打擊。<br />\n<br />\n報告又指，即使美、台軍隊能部份抵抗來自中國大陸的進攻，但大規模及長時間的進攻模式將令美台防禦變得複雜。加上解放軍已具備爭奪台灣附近的空中優勢，美軍介入台灣已無優勢可言；解放軍亦具備干擾美國偵察活動和訊息系統的能力，可創造出攻台的條件。<br />\n<br />\n此外，美國國務卿蒂勒森前日出訪拉丁美洲前發表演說，警告拉美國家要提防中國的「掠奪式」投資，更與「歐洲殖民主義」作比較。蒂勒森指，中國近年以經濟國策在拉丁美洲建立影響力，「中國的國家主導發展模式只會讓人聯想起過去，這不應是西半球的未來。我們一定要奮力抵禦那些遙遠的強權，他們並不反映本地的共同基本價值」。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社"},{"pid":"cec1feefee8d524c2654ba1a6887e6f1a3ad6889","tid":548804,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T04:25:14.000Z","msg":"屌，一登岸把台狗都爭住開腿等屌啦"},{"pid":"d4bb8466d5cc283d90e303a0cc1358578c1fcb2a","tid":548804,"uid":9694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T05:25:47.000Z","msg":"美國一面叫盟友停止被支那經濟侵略，法國英國卻爭先恐後地加大同中國既互相投資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daaf3a860e2f238be7121a82ee0588a425ca6a69","tid":548804,"uid":87573,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T05:35:54.000Z","msg":"空襲d人民幣已經贏左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee523c07205f8e7e0c8ece7e6774daaaa5b6bb33","tid":548804,"uid":53498,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T05:42:32.000Z","msg":"世界末日都唔敢打啦,口交部鳩噏就叻"},{"pid":"44b646cab519d01298ebed8a3083f2a12f8dd07e","tid":548804,"uid":41509,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T05:44:59.000Z","msg":"仲有人信會打仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f6a65cda04cc5e84408718622b44cb62d5db480","tid":548804,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T05:55:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f58049d58abedf2d28428e6cd91628d21bafa704","tid":548804,"uid":53577,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T06:00:18.000Z","msg":"大陸點樣打台海吖，一登陸已經比台灣用雷霆2000雲爆彈炸成炮灰。<br />\n<br />\n就算講人海戰術台灣有幾百萬人等住你，反而你大陸運到十萬人上岸已經係奇蹟。"},{"pid":"2d3eb749792e9769f312bbea82f8d3f91ae00c01","tid":548804,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T06:01:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a5b1f01ab6b35981ed815a2faa81c2071033e2b3","tid":548804,"uid":54373,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T06:08:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180203/20293960\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180203%2F20293960&d=zRDvmxCS8mYNeMIDAQYKsV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=14ed200d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180203%2F20293960&h=0cee1e9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180203/20293960</a><br />\n<strong>美智庫：20